          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2015-10-05T19:11:57Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Amends Rule XIV (Order and Priority of Business) of the Rules of the House of Representatives to require the House to be in session at least: (1) 40 hours each week other than a week that is designated as a district work period, and (2) 8 hours per day for the remaining days of any week in which a legal holiday occurs (other than such designated week).</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2015-10-01T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
